data.description: Welcome to serenity 15 minutes from Missoula! This lovely Frenchtown Valley home is for sale for the first time, and is awaiting your personal touches! The home sits on over 1.5 acres, and has plenty of space for all your needs, with 6 bedrooms total, and 5 bathrooms. The basement can serve as a living space for extra family or potential rental income. You will find plenty of storage, an office, a hobby room, formal dining room, sitting room, library loft and so much more! The views are beautiful, and you will enjoy sitting on your from or back deck to enjoy your favorite beverage or book.  Contact Kerry Lehman at (406)370-0395 or your real estate professional.
